#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:202
msgid "**产品名称必须唯一**：重复名称将导致创建失败，需修改后重试。"
msgstr ""
"**Product name must be unique**: a duplicate name fails creation; change it "
"and retry."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:203
msgid "**向导不支持断点续建**：若中途退出向导，无法返回之前的步骤。请删除未完成的产品后重新创建。"
msgstr ""
"**The wizard does not support resume-from-checkpoint**: exiting partway "
"through means you cannot return to earlier steps. Delete the half-finished "
"product and start again."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:204
msgid "**DIP 检测默认关闭**：需手动在 **自动编程检测类型：** 中展开并勾选 DIP 子类（炉前或炉后）才会激活 DIP 参数区域。"
msgstr ""
"**DIP inspection is off by default**: expand **Auto-Programming inspection "
"types**, check a DIP sub-class (pre-wave or post-wave) and the DIP parameter"
" block activates."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:205
msgid "**桥接检测默认关闭**：勾选 **桥接** 复选框后，**邻近距离 (像素)** 参数方可编辑；默认值为 0（禁用）。"
msgstr ""
"**Bridge inspection is off by default**: once you check **Bridge**, "
"**Adjacency distance (pixels)** becomes editable. The default is 0 "
"(disabled)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:206
msgid "**健康检查建议保持开启**：两项健康检查（数量检查、质量检查）默认开启，可帮助在自动编程完成后验证 ROI 质量。"
msgstr ""
"**Keep health checks on**: both Count check and Quality check are on by "
"default and help verify ROI quality after Auto-Programming."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:208
msgid "**创建产品常见问题与排查**"
msgstr "**Common questions and troubleshooting when creating a product**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:210
msgid ""
"**完整拍摄图像拼接异常**：检查 PCB 在采集过程中是否发生移动/震动；若确认无移动，可能为相机标定失准，请执行 :ref:`相机现场校准` "
"后重拍。"
msgstr ""
"**Full-capture image shows stitching artifacts**: check whether the PCB "
"shifted or vibrated during capture. If the board was stable, the camera "
"calibration may have drifted — run :ref:`相机现场校准` and re-capture."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:211
msgid "**创建产品提示\"传送带占用\"**：确认是否有正在运行的检测任务或未释放的产品锁；若无任务仍显示占用，可重启软件刷新状态。"
msgstr ""
"**Create-Product reports \"conveyor in use\"**: check for a running "
"inspection session or a product lock that wasn't released. If nothing is "
"running and it still reports the conveyor as in use, restart the software to"
" refresh state."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:212
msgid "**退出向导后无法回到中途步骤**：当前版本不支持断点续建，只能删除该未完成产品后重新创建。"
msgstr ""
"**Exiting the wizard leaves no way back to an intermediate step**: resume is"
" not supported in this release — delete the half-finished product and start "
"over."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:214
msgid "**相关页面**"
msgstr "**Related pages**"

